<h1>Styleguide</h1>

<p>
	The living design system of this site. Guiding principle:
	<strong>truth to mediums</strong> — what lives on a screen should be
	inherently of the screen. Nothing here imitates paper, plastic, or any
	other material.
</p>

<h2>Seed palette</h2>

<p>Four immutable seeds, chosen by hand. Every other color is a declared, quantized derivation of these.</p>

